item.title: Ginisang Monggo
item.description: Mung beans cooked with pork belly strips, bitter gourd leaves INGREDIENTS 250 grams monggo (mung beans) 1⁄4 kg. pork belly, cut in to chunks 3 gloves garlic 1 big onion 2 medium tomatoes ampalaya leaves patis cooking oil 1.5 liters of water (use for pre-boiling the beans)
